          </identifier>
          <title>
            <string language="en">Kate Chopin: A Re-Awakening</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Kate Chopin: Re-Awakening</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Kate Chopin : Un Réveil</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Kate Chopin: Re-Awakening</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Kate Chopin: Una Rianimazione</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Kate chopin: Μια αναζωπύρωση</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Kate Chopin: Una Despertar</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">revisits the life and work of this 19th-century Louisiana author whose story of a woman's self-realization, The Awakening, shocked the Victorian establishment and devastated her own career.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Arts</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">besucht das Leben und die Arbeit dieses 
19th-century Louisiana Autors nochmals dessen Geschichte der 
Selbst-Realisierung einer Frau, das Wecken, die viktorianisch Einrichtung
und verwüstet ihrer eigenen Karriere entsetzte.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">revisite la vie et le travail de cet auteur de 
19th-century Louisiane dont l'histoire du art de l'auto-portrait-realization d'une 
femme, le réveil, a choqué l'établissement victorien et dévasté
sa propre carrière.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">revisita a vida e o trabalho deste autor de 
19th-century Louisiana cuja a história do self-self-realization de 
uma mulher, awakening, chocou o estabelecimento de Victorian e 
devastated sua própria carreira.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">rivisita la vita ed il lavoro di questo autore di 
19th-century Luisiana di cui la storia di auto-realizzazione della 
donna, il risveglio, ha scosso l'istituzione di Victorian e devastante
la sua propria carriera.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">ξαναεπισκέπτεται τη ζωή και την εργασία αυτού του 
συντάκτη της Λουιζιάνας 19$ος-αιώνα η ο οποίος ιστορία της 
μόνος-πραγματοποίησης μιας γυναίκας, το ξύπνημα, συγκλόνισε τη 
βικτοριανή καθιέρωση και κατάστρεψε τη σταδιοδρομία της.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">revisita la vida y el trabajo de este autor de 
19th-century Luisiana que historia de la uno mismo-realizacio'n de una
mujer, el despertar, dio una sacudida eléctrica el establecimiento de
Victorian y devastado su propia carrera.</string>
          </description>
